hopobject.body: How long are you planning to stay here? spetton hexskin lycra In the Rose Garden, President Obama called the crisis the consequence of an ideological crusade against the Affordable Care Act. (He spoke surrounded by Americans who will benefit from the health care marketplaces, which, by happenstance, were opening Tuesday.) He said he would not give in to unreasonable demands by "one faction of one party of one house of Congress in one branch of government."
